title: StanChart resumes dividend but revenues disappoint
text:
StanChart resumes dividend but revenues disappoint 1:53pm GMT - 01:35 
Standard Chartered resumes paying dividends after posting a six-fold jump in annual pretax profit, but weaker-than-expected revenue dampens any celebration from investors. David Pollard
